Mockup Description for Inventory Manager (Version 2 - Improved Layout)

Improved layout for Inventory Manager.

Changes:
- High-density table with better column organization
- Expandable side panels for details
- Added bulk actions toolbar

Layout:
- Top: Advanced filters and bulk actions
- Center: Enhanced data table with inline editing
- Side: Detailed view panel

Hierarchy:
- Primary: Data table with actions
- Secondary: Filters and details

Usability:
- Inline editing, better sorting options